def reverseKGroup(head, k):
    if not head:
        return None
    dummy = ListNode(0)
    dummy.next = head
    pre = dummy
    while head:
        cur = head
        for _ in range(k):
            if not cur.next:
                return dummy.next
            cur = cur.next
        next_node = cur
        cur = pre.next
        for _ in range(k):
            temp = cur.next
            cur.next = next_node
            next_node = temp
            cur = temp
        pre.next = next_node
        head = cur
    return dummy.next
